The fork replaces the data table viewer (client/src/webview/* and
client/src/panels/DataViewer.ts) with an independent re-implementation
modeled after the look and feel of the Microsoft mssql VS Code extension's
results grid (https://github.com/Microsoft/vscode-mssql, MIT license). No
source from the mssql extension is included; behavior parity was achieved
by clean-room re-implementation against publicly observable UX.

All file-level copyright headers in unchanged upstream files are preserved.
New files contributed by this fork carry their own header.
